🧩 How to Install Shadows of Valour
Download the archive you prefer (.rar or .zip) from the latest release.

Create a new folder anywhere on your drive (e.g., C:\Games\ShadowsOfValour).

Extract all files from the archive into this folder.

Run the game by launching:
Shadows of Valour.exe

✅ Play and enjoy the experience! ⚔️

❗ Troubleshooting & Notes
If the game doesn’t launch properly or you encounter bugs, feel free to contact me or open an issue on this repo.

This is my first complete project, and I’ve done my best to polish it and fix all known issues.
Any feedback is welcome and helps me grow as a developer!

